These solutions are still clunky. In the US, for example, WhatsApp carts do=
n=E2=80=99t support payments, so businesses and customers need to arrange p=
ayments separately. But Facebook recently rolled out WhatsApp payments in I=
ndia, where it is the country=E2=80=99s SuperApp, after years of government=
 pushback. Facebook=E2=80=99s $5.8 billion investment in Reliance=E2=80=99s=
 Jio Platforms [https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVUMtuwyAQ_JpwswUYbOfAIZ=
f-hoVhcVbBYPFo5H59aSK1qrSrlXY0OztjdIEtplMdMRdSM6QFrWIjnwcprsQqYdksZ4J5cQlg1=
-hVSRXIUVePRheM4cWglEtyV0bLmWtnB6upcWKSMzgujJmYWN1sDfnRWXS1CMGAgk9IZwxAvLqX=
