jX4cs4QlF7BfiIpnxDvD8u5g7zOXKEUSB-y5UQFpQMevlBzs7HFGf6N_gDDjokC] in iOS 14 =
which will hurt Facebook=E2=80=99s ability to collect data and target custo=
mers in apps.
TikTok may steal attention, the lifeblood of an Aggregator, from Facebook, =
or at the very least, hamper its ability to acquire young users.=C2=A0
But Facebook is undervalued relative to any set of peers, and that=E2=80=99=
s before taking its bets on the future into consideration. In the near-term=
, it is unifying messaging, social, and commerce in the most ambitious back=
ward integration in history. Long-term, it may become the platform on which=
 the Virtual Reality economy is built. And we got through this without ment=
ioning Facebook=E2=80=99s crypto project (currently: Diem [https://email.mg=
2.substack.com/c/eJxFUcuO5CAM_JrkRkQgrz5wGGl3TvMPEQGnY3UCETjTm_36dbpHWgnZMo=
Upl8tZgntMp9ljpvLIkEb0pu7UoNvmVnrT-HpohxLzOCeAzeJqKB1Q7se0orOEMbw6pFRtuZimb=
