</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 1em 0;">As it continues to connect its various platforms and integrate=
 more commerce and payments functionality, Facebook will complete the most =
ambitious backward integration in history, from ads into eCommerce. It will=
