ck, buy, or talk to a person (or AI) to answer any questions. If Facebook p=
ulls off that vision, <strong>it will have its own Everywhere Store to batt=
le Amazon&#8217;s Everything Store</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1=
a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Oh yeah, and=
 one more thing&#8230;&nbsp;</p><h3 style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-family: '=
SF Compact Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto,=
