/strong>Facebook lowered the price point for the Oculus Quest 2, it&#8217;s=
 newest VR headset, to $299, and pre-orders surpassed the original Oculus&#=
8217; by 5x. Oculus Quest 2 is the best standalone headset on the market, a=
