ght: 26px; margin: 0;"><strong>AR Glasses. </strong>Facebook has plans to r=
elease AR glasses next year, in partnership with Luxottica. Early attempts =
to build AR glasses -- from Google Glass to Snap Lenses -- have ranged from=
 butt-of-joke to toy-like, but if Facebook can marry what&#8217;s worked in=
 Oculus with the lighter touch needed for AR, it has a shot.&nbsp;</p></li>=
</ul><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
: 0 0 1em 0;">Just like Facebook&#8217;s social apps, the Facebook Reality =
