></h3><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margi=
n: 0 0 1em 0;">Facebook is hard to love. Concerns around privacy and antico=
mpetitive behavior abound, it rips off other companies&#8217; product work,=
